                    Requests</link>
                or
                <link xlink:href="http://docs.rackspace.com/networks/api/v2/cn-devguide/content/section_pagination.html">Pagination 
                    of Requests</link>
                in the <citetitle>Cloud Networks API Developer Guide</citetitle>.</para>
        </wadl:doc>
